      • addEdge

        public boolean addEdge(Node from,
                       Node to)
        If no Edge exists between the given Nodes Creates a new Edge object between the given Nodes Adds the Edge to the adjacency list Updates the in and out degrees of the Nodes If Nodes do not already exist, creates them
        Parameters:
        from - Node that the edge should start from
        to - Node that the edge should point to
        Returns:
        True if an Edge was successfully added, False if Edge already exists

      • addNode

        public boolean addNode(java.lang.String value)
        If no Node exists with given value Creates a new Node object Adds the Node to the adjacency list increments the node count
        Parameters:
        value - The value to be given to the new node
        Returns:
        True if a Node was successfully added, False if Node already exists or value is incorrect length
